data.description: What a find,  charming and spacious comfortable home in amazing condition.  Gorgeous flooring in common areas, and carpet in the bedrooms.  Neutral paint tones throughout the interior.  Cozy covered back patio and big backyard.  Main Bedroom and En-suite are spacious boasting a jacuzzi tub and two walk in closets. Fence is on a concrete slab perimeter, storage shed also on a concrete slab.
